flowchart TD
    Browser[Browser UI]
    SocketIO[Socket.IO Client]
    Server[Flask + SocketIO Server]
    Game[Tetris Game State]
    Renderer[Canvas Renderer]
    Input[Player / Bot Input]
    Gravity[Gravity Tick]
    Update[State Update Event]
    Render[Render Frame]

    Input -->|keyboard / bot| SocketIO
    SocketIO -->|emit move/rotate/hard_drop| Server
    Server -->|update game state| Game
    Gravity -->|emit gravity| SocketIO
    SocketIO -->|gravity event| Server
    Game -->|new state| Update
    Server -->|emit state| SocketIO
    SocketIO -->|receive state| Browser
    Browser -->|draw board| Renderer
    Browser -->|update UI| Render
    Game -->|lock / clear lines| Game
    Update -->|refresh UI| Render
    Server -->|uses game logic| Game
